-- out/todo.txt --
Structural cycle error positions differ between v2 and v3: v2 includes an
extra structural cycle at ./in.cue:3:25 (fibRec reference) for fib3/fib7/fib12;
v3 reports positions at in.cue:8:9 and in.cue:8:38 only. Functionally both
versions correctly report fib1=1, fib2=1, and fib3/fib7/fib12 as errors.
